<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Due to a bug in Zend_Http_Client (ZF-8057) disabling authentication on the HTTP client before setting the URI results in a fatal error and thus making the whole class pretty useless. The simple workaround for the issue is to call Zend_Http_Client::setUri() before calling any other method of the object.</p>

